class\nof brane models the Standard Model is realized as a GUT with its intestines\nremoved, to keep only the good parts: a GUT without guts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jan 2014 19:24:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2014 12:15:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
